# Keep the build context tight and don't leak secrets.
#
# Note: this file lives in seeme/ but the build context is the parent
# diagrams/ folder, so paths are relative to that.

# Local installs / build output — re-installed inside the image
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage

# Secrets — never bake an env file into an image
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# VCS / editor cruft
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.log

# Tests aren't needed at runtime (fixtures ARE — they power `seeme example`)
seeme/test/*.test.ts

# Docker meta itself
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/docker
